Ana haɓaka yawan haɗarin cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Tatalin Arzikin Yankin Turai da Ingila, ran 1 ga watan Janairu zuwa ran 15 watan Maris 2020
Lamarin da ya haifar da cututtukan Coronavirus (COVID-19) yana nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin tattalin arzikin Turai da Ingila da ke tabbatar da cewa, yayin da a wani matakin daban dangane da ƙasar, cutar ta COVID-19 tana ci gaba cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Dangane da shaida daga Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da rukunin kulawa mai zurfi ya kamata su ƙara shiryawar su don karuwar marasa lafiyar COVID-19 waɗanda zasu buƙaci kiwon lafiya, kuma musamman kulawa mai zurfi.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba 2019, an ba da rahoton wani tarin cututtukan huhu da ba a san ilimin halittar sa ba a Wuhan, Lardin Hubei, kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga watan Janairu shekara 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cuta ta kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton wakili da ke kawo sabon cutar coronavirus ne wanda aka mai da shi a matsayin cutar hanyoyin numfashi mai tsananin coronavirus 2 (SARS-COV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 an sanya mata suna cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Shaida zuwa yau ita ce ca 80% na mutane tare da COVID-19 suna da cuta mai laushi, wato kamuwa da cutar hanyoyin numfashi tare da ko ba tare da cutar huhu ba, kuma yawancin waɗannan suna samun sauki.
A cikin kashi 14% masu cututtuka, COVID-19 yana haɓaka cikin mummunan cutar da ke buƙatar kwana a asibiti yayin da raguwar kashi 6% suna fuskantar mummunan cutar da ke buƙatar kulawa mai zurfi.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya a asibiti sakamakon COVID-19 ya kai ca kashi 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, muna tantance sauye-sauye game da abin da ya faru na COVID-19 a cikin kowace Europeanasashen Turai / Yankin Turai na Yankin Turai (EU/EEA) da Kingdomasar Ingila (Birtaniya) tare da kwatanta su da na lardin Hubei, Sin.
Hakanan muna kwatanta adadin masu kamuwa da cutarbCOVID-19 a kasachen EU/EEA da UK tare da na Italiya lokacin ranar 31 ga watan Janairu - ranar 15 ga watan Maris 2020.
Lamuran cutar COVID-19 a kasashen EU / EEA da UK
Bayan kasar Sin, COVID-19 ya ci gaba da yaduwar kasashe daban-daban da kuma saurin annban COVID-19 a cikin sauran duniya a halin yanzu tana bin wannan kasar.
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar ta ranar 5 ga watan Maris na Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. wanda aka ba da rahoto game da Turai ta farko ta tabbatar da lamarin cutar COVID-19 bisa ga bayyanar lamarin WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta gabatar da farko lamarin cutar guda uku a ranar 24 ga watan Janairu 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, Lardin Hubei, Kasar Sin.
Kamar yadda yake a ranar 15 ga watan Maris 2020, an gano lamarin cutar COVID-19 a cikin dukkan ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da UK, inda tsakanin ranar 31 ga watan Disamba 2019 kuma wannan ranar ta haɗa, masun kamu da cutar 39,768 da mutuwar mutane 1,727 wanda aka ruwaito, tare da lamarin 17,750. da mutuwar mutane 1,441 daga Italiya kadai.
Samun lambar tarawa da tarawar abin da ya faru na masun cututtukar COVID-19
A Cibiyar Yaki da Cututtuka ta Yankin Turai (ECDC), an sanar da ƙididdigar COVID-19 a cikin kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka samo daga kawai kafofin hukuma kamar ma'aikatar lafiya ta ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na WHO da WHO, ana sabunta su. kowace rana da karfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da waɗannan bayanan don tantance halaye na COVID-19 a EU/EEA da UK, da kwatanta su da na Italiya.
A matsayin wakili na abubuwan da ke faruwa na lamuran COVID-19, mun kirga kwanaki 14 tarawar abin da ya faru da aka yanke na lamurar COVID-19, don haka yin la’akari da tafarkin COVID-19, a cikin kowace kasar EU/EEA da Ingila, tsakanin ranar 1 ga watan Janairu - 15 Maris 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da tarawar lambar sanarwa game da lamarin kamuwa da cutan a kowace kasa a ranar 15 ga watan Maris 2020 8:00 na safe idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya a ranar 31 ga watan Janairu - ranar 15 ga watan Maris 2020.
Hanyar COVID-19 cikin kasachen EU/EEA da Ingila
Sauye a cikin kwanaki 14 tarawar tsayar da abin da ya faru na lamarin cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK gaba ɗaya sun bi ta lardin Hubei (Sin) (Siffa 1).
Don EU/EEA da Ingila gaba ɗaya, yawan abin da ya faru na COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa kusan ran 21 ga watan Fabrairu sannan kuma ya karu sosai a kusa da ranar 28 ga watan Fabrairu 2020 (kayan kari abubuwa).
Wannan ya jawu ta yawan saurin karuwa cikin lambar rahoton lamarin cutar daga Italiya, amma duk sauran kasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya sun nuna irin wannan yanayin na kara yawan abubuwan COVID-19 (Karin kaya).
Siffa 2 yana nuna lamarin cutar COVID-19, a cikin EU/EEA da UK idan aka kwatanta da wannan a Italiya na ranar 31 ga watan Janairu - ranar 15 ga watan Maris 2020.
Yana nuna cewa, kamar yadda a ranar 15 ga watan Maris kafe 8:00 na safe, wasu ƙasashe EU/EEA 15 da Ingila sun riga sun bayar da rahoton masu kamuwa da cutar kwatanta da na Italiya kafin makonni 3 da suka shige ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakon binciken mu ya nuna cewa lambar masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 yana karuwa cikin hanzari a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Abubuwan lura da aka gani a cikin abin da ya faru na COVID-19 sun ba da shawarar cewa annobar ta ci gaba da sauri a cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan duk da cewa ƙasashe sun kasance a matakai daban-daban, a cikin martanin lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa, kuma mai yiwuwa ƙararraki daban-daban a cikin ƙasashe da ƙa'idodi daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya waɗanda dole ne a gwada su don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da samun gwaji.
A farkon Maris 2020, likitoci a yankuna da abin ya shafa na Italiya sun baiyana halin da ake ciki inda ca 10% na marasa lafiya da COVID-19 suka buƙaci kulawa mai zurfi kuma kafofin watsa labaru sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da rukunin kulawa mai zurfi a cikin waɗannan yankuna sun riga sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
Bayanai game da kai marasa lafiya a asibiti don COVID-19 da/ko sashin kulawa mai zurfi a halin yanzu akwai a matakin EU/EEA don kawai kashi 6% da kashi 1% lamarin cutar, bi da bi (bayanan ba su nuna ba).
Yakamata, duk da haka, a tattara su ta hanyar tsari don dacewa da bayanan sa ido na halin yanzu wanda ya mayar da hankali kan rahoton masu kamu da cutar da kuma yawan mutuwa.
Nazarin da aka yi a shekara ta 2010 zuwa 11 ya nuna babban bambanci a cikin kasancewar kulawa mai zurfi da gadaje na kulawa a Turai, kama daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa gadaje 4.2 ga yawan jama’a 100,000 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun albarkatu ko ƙasa fiye da Italiya (12.5 kulawa mai zurfi da gadaje na kulawar dai-dai da cikin yawan jama’a 100,000 cikin 2010-11).
Yanayin tsarafawa wanda ya danganta ga cikawar cibiyoyin kiwon lafiya, da ƙididdigar kowace ƙasar EU/EEA da UK da mamayar zaman asibiti domin lamarin cutar COVID-19 wanda ya hadu da &gt; > 90% da hadarin fi yawan gadon kulawa, an samar da su a sabuntawa ta shida na ECDC saurin kimantawar hadari kan COVID-19.
Tunda yake masun kamuwa da cutan a tare cikin wasu yakin kasashen EU/EEA da UK, da asibitoci da kuma rukunin kulawa mai zurfin yawancin lokaci na taimaki jama’ar yankin da aka sani, bayanai game da lamarin cututtuka da gadajen kulawa zai fi dacewa a samo su a matakin Nomenclature na raka’ar yankunan ƙasa don ƙidaya 2 (NUTS-2) mataki.
Koyi daga Italiya da abubuwan da ake samu a halin yanzu a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Ingila.
Kasashe, asibitoci da rukunin kulawa mai zurfi ya kamata su shirya kansu don yanayin watsawar al'umma na SARS-CoV-2 da karuwa a yawan masu haƙuri da COVID-19 waɗanda ke buƙatar kiwon lafiya, da kuma kulawa ta musamman, kamar wanda ke faruwa. a cikin yankunan da Italiya ta shafa.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin ƙididdigar haɓakar haɗari na ECDC na baya-bayan nan, saurin aiki, cikakken aiki da cikakken tsari yana da mahimmanci don jinkirta yaduwar SARS-COV-2, tare da canzawa daga haɓakawa zuwa tsarin ragewa, kamar yadda saurin karuwa a yawan masu kamuwa da cutar ba zai iya samar da masun bada shawara da cikaken lokaci ma asibitoci domin fahimta, karba da daidaita hanyar aiwatarwa kafin lokacin.
Binciken saurin haɗari ya kuma lissafa matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin annoban.
Akwai gajeriyar tagar dama a yayin da ƙasashe ke da damar ƙara yawan ƙoƙarinsu na sarrafawa don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin kiwon lafiya.
Fadar da wannan, wataƙila tsarin kiwon lafiyar na wasu ƙasashe EU/EEA zai iya fuskantar yawan marasa lafiya waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai zurfi a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa ko makonni masu zuwa.
