Ambulaf ta kara daurin (S) glycoprotein a masu karɓar kwayar halittar sa angiotensin-mai canza enzyme 2 (ACE2) da pepeididly peptidase 4 (DPP4) don SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, bi da bi, sannan kuma hadawar membrane yana faruwa.
An saki kwayar cutar RNA a cikin cytoplasm; bayan sake fasaltar kwayar halittar, RNA genomic rufe baya da ambulaf na glycofurotin da sunadarai na nucleocapsid suna samar da virion-dauke da vesicles, wanda sai ya hadu da membrane na plasma don sakin kwayar cutan.
An bayar da rahoton jerin kwayoyin halitta na farko na SARS-CoV-2 a ran 10 ga watan Janairu, 2020.
An gano SARS-CoV-2 wani sabon nau'in beta-CoV ne tare da fiye da kashi 99.98% asalin kwayoyin halitta tsakanin samfuran 10 da aka tattara daga asalin yaduwar, Kasuwar abincin teku ta Huanan a Wuhan.
SARS-CoV-2 ya fi kamani da SARS-CoV fiye da MERS-CoV.
Ta hanyar watsa microscopy na wutar lantarki, an samo barbashi na SARS-CoV-2 a sassan iskar jikin mutum na epithelium.
An samo ACE2 na mutum a matsayin mai karɓa wa SARS-CoV-2 kazalika da SARS-CoV.
Duk da haka, furotin S na SARS-CoV-2 ya danganta ga ACE2 na ɗan adam fiye da na SARS-CoV, wanda ya zo daidai da gaskiyar cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana haifar da ƙarancin kamuwa da cuta a cikin marasa lafiya fiye da SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 na iya samar da gajeriyar sunadarin furotin da aka shigar ta orf3b da wani furotin da ke rufe da orf8.
orf3b na SARS-CoV-2 na iya taka rawa a cikin bada kwayar cuta da kuma hana bayyanar IFNβ; kodayake, orf8 ba ya da wani yanki da aka sani aiki ko motif.
A ranar 18 ga watan Fabrairu, 2020, Zhou, et al, sun ba da rahoton tsarin cryo-EM na cikakken ACE2 na dan adam a ƙudurin 2.9 Å ƙuduri cikin hadadden mai ɗaukar amino acid B0AT1.
Sun gano cewa hadadden, wanda an gano aka bude kuma an rufe, an taru a matsayin sinadari dimer kuma hadadden ACE2-B0AT1 na iya daurar sinadarai biyu na S furotin, wanda ke ba da shaida don ganewar CoV da kamuwa da cuta.
B0AT1 na iya zama makasudin warkewa don gwajin magunguna don murƙushe kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Asalin da kuma tsakiyar mazaman cutar.
An san cewa SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV sun samo asali ne daga jemagu kuma ana watsa su ga mutane ta hanyar kuliyoyi da raƙuma.
Ta hanyar kwatancen fitowar cututtukan na SARS-CoV-2 tare da sauran CoVs, an yi la’akari cewa jemage ne mazaunin SARS-CoV-2 kamar yadda sabon ƙwayar cuta ya kasance kashi 96% zuwa mai kamar-SARS CoVs biyu daga jemagu da ake kira bat-SL-CoVZX45 da jemage-SL-CoVZX21.
Duk da haka, wande mazaman tsakiya mai taimaka wa kwayar cutar ta keta shingen nau'ikan don kama mutane har yanzu ba a san shi ba, kuma har yanzu ba a fara sanin hanyar yada cutar ba.
Ji, et al., Sun gabatar da macizai a matsayin jigilar kwayar cutar daga jemagu zuwa mutane wanda ke da alaƙar yin ma'amala tsakanin S furotin.
Dangane da wani bincike, masu bincike a Guangzhou, China, sun ba da shawarar cewa pangolins - dogon-hanci da baki, dabbobi masu cin kyashi an cikia amfani da su cikin al’adar maganin Sinawa - su ne mazama SARS-COV-2 da ke yiwu wa bisa ga kashi 99% kwayar halitta a cikin wani CoV wanda aka gano a cikin pangolins da SARS-CoV-2.
Duk da haka bambancin kashi 1% ya bazu akan kwayoyin halitta guda biyu har yanzu babban bambanci ne; don haka, ana jiran sakamako na ƙarshe don tabbataccen hujja (Fig.(Fig.33).
Sunadarain kimiyyar kadarorin SARS-CoV-2 har yanzu ba a san su ba.
SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV zasu iya rayuwa cikin kwalban gwaji na tsawon awanni 48 a cikin busheshen yanayin har zuwa kwanaki 5 a ƙarƙashin 20 ° C da danshi kashi 40% -50%.
SARS-CoV-2 na iya mallakar kaddarorin iri daya.
An ba da rahoton cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana kula da haskoki na zafin rana da zafi a 56 ° C na minti 30; kashi 75% ethanol, chlorine-mai dauke da sinadarai, sinadarin peracetic acid, chloroform, da sauran abubuwan rage kiba, amma ba chlorhexidine ba, na iya lalata kwayar ta yadda ya kamata.
Yawan mutane gabaɗaya sun rasa garkuwa ga SARS-CoV-2 kuma saboda haka ana iya kamuwa da sabuwar ƙwaya cutan.
A halin yanzu, babu cikakken binciken da aka bayar da rahoton game da amsawar rigakafi ga SARS-CoV-2.
Don haka, zamu iya komawa ne kawai ga binciken da muka gabata akan wasu CoVs, musamman SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV (Fig. (Fig. 4).4).
Gabaɗaya, bayan da kwayar cutar ta mamaye mai watsa shiri, an fara gane ta hanyar rigakafin garkuwar jiki ta hanyar karɓa (PRRs) gami da masu karɓa na nau'in irin-C, kamar-Toll mai karɓa (TLR), mai karɓar kamar-NOD mai karɓa (NLR) , da kamar-RIG-I mai karɓa (RLR).
Ta hanyar hanyoyi daban-daban, kwayar cutar ta haifar da bayyanar da abubuwan da ke haifar da kumburi, matattarar ƙwayoyin dendritic, da haɓaka nau'in I interferons (IFNs) waɗanda ke iyakance yaduwar ƙwayar cuta kuma suna haɓaka matakan ƙwayoyin cuta na ƙwayoyin cuta.
Duk da haka, sinadarin furotin N na SARS-CoV zai iya taimakawa kwayar cutar ta tsere daga amsawar garkuwan jiki.
Ba da daɗewa ba, amsar rigakafin ƙwayar cuta ta shiga cikin yaƙi da ƙwayar cuta.
T lymphocytes ciki har da CD4 + da CD8 + T tantanin halitta suna taka muhimmiyar rawa a cikin tsaron.
Tantanin halita CD4 + T suna motsa ƙwayoyin B don samar da ƙayyadaddun rigakafin ƙwayoyin cuta, kuma sel CD8 + T tantanin halita na kashe kwayoyin cutar da suka kamu da ciwo kai tsaye.
Mai taimakon tantanin halita T ta samar da cytokines na kumburi don taimakawa kwayoyin da ke kare su.
Duk da haka, CoV zai iya hana ayyukan tantanin halita T ta hanyar gabatar da apoptosis na tantanin halita T.
Rigakafin ƙwaƙwalwar ciki har da haɗi kamar C3a da C5a da ƙwayoyin garkuwar jiki suna da mahimmanci don yaƙar kamuwa da cuta.
Alal misali, warewar kwayoyin garkuwar jiki daga wani mara lafiya mai warkewa ya watsar da MERS-CoV.
A gefe guda, wuce gona da iri na tsarin rigakafi yana haifar da babban adadin radadi kyauta a cikin gida wanda zai iya haifar da lahani ga huhu da sauran gabobin, kuma, a cikin mummunan yanayin, gazawar ƙwayoyin cuta da dama har ma da mutuwa.
Kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2, wanda aka nuna ta hanyar haɗuwa, yana yuwuwar kama tsofaffi masun zama da wasu cututtuka da mata masu juna biyu.
Abu ne gama gari cewa ga mutanen da ke kamuwa da ɗimbin ƙwayoyin cuta ko waɗanda aka keɓance ayyukan su, suna da damar da za su kamu da ita fiye da sauran.
An kiyasta cewa lokacin girman SARS-CoV-2 shine ranakun 1-14, yawancin kwanaki 3-7 bisa ya danganta ga binciken farkon mutane 425 wanda suka kamu da cutar cikin Wuhan.
Duk da haka, binciken akan mutane 1,099 masu cutan ya nuna cewa kwanakin haifarwa shine kwana 3 a matsakaita kuma daga ranakun 0 zuwa 24.
Wani ƙarin binciken da aka yi kwanan nan, ya nuna cewa lokacin shiryawa ya kasance kwanaki 4.8 (3.0-7.2) kwanaki bisa ga tarihin kamuwar mutane 8,866.
Yana da matukar muhimmanci ga hukumomin kiwon lafiya su daidaita lokacin keɓancewa daidai gwargwado lokacin shiryayye, don haka hana kamuwa da cuta amma mutanen da ba su da kwayar cutar kwayar cutar ga wasu.
A matsayin al’adar yau da kulum, mutanen da ke a fili, ko masu kamuwa da cutar, yawanci ana buƙatar ware kansu na kwanaki 14.
