Zazzabi shine babban kuma farkon nuna alamar COVID-19, wanda za'a iya haɗa shi ba tare da wata alama ba ko wasu alamomi kamar bushewar tari, gajeruwar numfashi, ciwon jijiyoyi, matsanancin ƙarfi, ciwon kai, ciwon makogwaro, rhinorrhea, ciwon kirji, zawo, tashin zuciya, da amarwa.
Wasu marasa lafiya sun sami dyspnea da / ko hypoxemia mako guda bayan farkon cutar.
A cikin mawuyacin hali, marasa lafiya sun sami saurin don haɓaka cutar hanyoyin numfashi mai tsanani, girgizawar jijiyoyin jiki, acidosis metabolic, da coagulopathy.
Marasa lafiya da zazzabi da/ko alamomin hanyoyin numfashi da zazzabi mai tsanani, koda ba tare da alamun cutar huhun ciki ba, yakamata a bincika kwayar cutan don gano shi da sauri.
Wani binciken alƙaluma a ƙarshen Disamba na 2019 ya nuna cewa kashiɗarin bayyanar cututtuka sun kasance kashi 98% ga zazzabi, kashi 76% don bushewar bushe, kashi 55% don dyspnea, da kashi 3% don zawo; 8% na marasa lafiya suna buƙatar tallafin iska.
An bayar da rahoton irin daya a cikin binciken biyu na kwanan nan game da tarin iyali da kuma tari wanda ya haifar ta hanyar watsawa daga mutum mai nunin alamar ciwon.
A kwatancewa, a binciken mutane a shekarar 2012 ya nuna cewa masu cutar MERS-CoV suma suna da zazzabi kashi (98%), bushewar tari kashi (47%), da dyspnea kashi (55%) a matsayin babban alamun su.
Duk da haka, kashi 80% daga cikinsu suna buƙatar tallafin shakar iska, fiye da marasa lafiyar COVID-19 kuma sun dace da mafi girmar kamuwar MERS fiye da na COVID-19.
An kuma lura da zawo kashi (26%) da ciwon makogwaro kashi (21%) tare da marasa lafiyar MERS.
A cikin marasa lafiya na SARS, an nuna cewa zazzabi kashi (99% -100%), tari mai bushewar kashi (29% -75%), dyspnea kashi (40% -42%), zawo kashi (20-25%), da ciwon makogwaro kashi (13 -25%) sune manyan alamu kuma ana buƙatar tallafin iska don kusan kashi 14% -20% na marasa lafiya.
Ya zuwa ranar 14 ga watan Fabrairu, mutuwar COVID-19 ya zama kashi 2% lokacin da aka tabbatar da masu kamuwa da chutar sun kai 66,576 a duk duniya.
Kwatancen, mutuwa don SARS daga Nuwamba 2002 shine kashi 10% na mutane 8,096 wanda aka tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar.
Ga MERS, dangane da binciken alƙaluma a watan Yuni na 2012, mutuwa ta kasance kashi 37% daga cikin 2,494 lamari da aka tabbatar.
Wani binciken da aka yi a baya ya ba da rahoton cewa R0 na SARS-CoV-2 ya yi sama da 6.47 tazarar amintace na kashi 95% (CI) na 5.71-7.23, yayin da R0 na SARS-CoV ya jera daga 2 zuwa 4 kawai.
An gabatar da kwatancen SARS-CoV-2 tare da MERS-CoV da SARA-CoV dangane da alamomin su, mace-mace, da kuma R0 a cikin Tebur Tebur1.1.
Abubuwan da ke sama suna ba da shawara cewa SARS-CoV-2 suna da iko mafi girma don yadawa fiye da MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV, amma ba shi da kasala fiye da na ƙarshen biyu.
Don haka, ya fi fuskantar kalubale sosai wajen shawo kan cutar SARS-CoV-2 fiye da MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV.
Gungura wuri daya yakan faru sau dayawa ne a cikin dangi guda ɗaya ko daga taro guda ɗaya ko abin hawa kamar jirgin ruwan.
Marasa lafiya galibi suna da tarihin tafiya ko zama a Wuhan ko wasu wuraren da cutar ta shafa ko kuma hulɗa da masu kamuwa da cuta ko kuma marasa lafiya a cikin makwanni biyu da suka gabata kafin an fara.
Duk da haka, an ba da rahoton cewa mutane na iya ɗaukar kwayar cutar ba tare da alamu fiye da makonni biyu ba sannan kuma warkewar marasa lafiyar da aka kwantar da su daga asibitoci na iya ɗaukar cutar ta sake, wanda ke aika ƙararrawa don ƙara lokacin keɓewa.
Marasa lafiya suna da daidai ko rage lambar yanki farin jini (musamman cututtukan lymphocytes) a farkon matakin.
Alal misali, lymphopenia tare da yawan farin jinin tantanin halita <4 × 109/L hade da yawan lymphocyte <1×109/L, kuma an daga matakan asotate aminotransferase da viremia a marasa lafiya guda 1,099 wanda suka kamu da COVID-19.
Matakin hanta da jijiyar enzymes da myoglobin sun karu a cikin jinin wasu marasa lafiya, kuma an karuwar furotin C-mai martani da dalakawarr erythrocyte a cikin jinin na yawancin marasa lafiya.
A cikin marasa lafiya da ke da tsananin cuta, matakin D-dimer, samfurin fibrin mai lalatawa da ke akwai cikin jini, ya haɓaka, kuma an rage adadin ƙwayar cutar ta lymphocyte.
Rashin lafiya cikin hoton rediyon kirji ana samun shi a cikin mafi yawan marasa lafiya na COVID-19 kuma an nuna su ta hanyar inuwa biyu na inuwa ko kuma gilashin ƙasa a cikin huhu.
Yawanci marasa lafiya kan haifar da ciwon huhu, raunin huhu mai tsanani, da cutar hanyoyin numfashi mai tsanani (ARDS).
Lokacin da ARDS ta faru, kumburin da ba a sarrafa shi ba, tara ruwa, da fibrosis mai ci gaba sun lalata mummunar musayar gas sosai.
Rashin daidaituwa na nau'in-I da nau'in-II na pneumocytes yana rage matakin surfactant kuma yana kara tashin hankali, ta haka ne rage ikon fadadar huhun da kara hadarin rushewar huhu.
Sabili da haka, binciken mafi munin hoton zuciya sau da yawa suna kama da mafi girman yanayin cutar.
A ranar 18 ga watan Fabrairu, 2020, bincike na farko na COVID-19 ya nuna rashin cancanci na pneumocytes, hyaline membrane, da kuma ƙwayar cuta ta mahaifa, da tantanin halita da yawa na ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin huhun masu cuta wanda ya mutu da cutar, ya yi daidai da yanayin kamuwar cutar makamacin ARDS da marasa lafiyar SARS da MERS.
Ganowar SARS-CoV-2 RNA ta hanyar juyawar sarkar polymerase wato (reverse-transcriptase) (RT-PCR) anyi amfani da shi azaman manyan ka'idojin gwajin cutar COVID-19.
Duk da haka, saboda kiyatsa girman babu-rashi, wanda zai iya hanzartawar annoban, an fara amfani da alamun bayyanar asibiti don ganewar asali (wanda bai dogara ga RT-PCR ba) kadai ba a kasar Sin a ranar 13 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
Hakanan irin wannan yanayin ya faru tare da bayyanar cutar SARS.
Sabili da haka, haɗuwa da tarihin cutar, bayyanar asibiti, dakin gwaji da kuma binciken radiyo yana da mahimmanci kuma wajibi ne don yin ingantaccen bincike.
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kungiyar Feng Zhang ta ba da bayanin wata hanyar yin amfani da fasahar SHERLOCK ta CRISPR don gano SARS-CoV-2, wanda ke gano ƙwayoyin SARS-CoV-2 RNA roba a 20 × 10-18 mol / L zuwa 200 × 10-18 mol / L (10-100 kwafa ta microliter na shigar) ta amfani da dipstick a cikin ƙasa da awa ɗaya ba tare da buƙatar bayyanin kayan aikin ba.
Da fatan, sabuwar dabarar za ta iya bunkasa hankali da kwanciyar hankali matukar an tabbatar cikin samfuran asibiti.
Saboda ƙarancin ƙwarewa tare da sabon labari na CoV, likitoci na iya samar da kulawa ta musamman ga marasa lafiyar COVID-19, yayin da ake ƙoƙarin hanyoyin jiyya da dama waɗanda aka yi amfani da su ko aka gabatar dasu don jiyyar wasu CoV kamar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV da sauran cututtukan (Tebur 2).2).
Wadannan hanyoyin jinya na yanzu da kuma yiwuwar jiyya tare da magungunan rigakafi, da immunosuppressants, steroids, plasma daga majinyatan da suka sami sauki, magungunan Sinawa, da tallafin tunani.
Ko da plasma daga majinyatan da sun samu sauki an gabatar dasu ne domin ayi amfani dasu don jiyya.
Kamfanonin magunguna suna yin tsere don haɓaka ƙwayoyin garkuwa da alluran rigakafin kan kwayar cutan.
SARS-CoV-2 suna kai hari sosai a huhu a farawa kuma mai yiwuwa kuma suna kaiwa hari, zuwa ƙarancin ƙima, sauran gabobin da ke bayyana ACE2, kamar tsarin gastrointestinal da kodan.
Duk da haka, lalatawar hanyar numfashi da gazawa sune babbar haɗari ga marasa lafiya da babban dalilin mutuwa.
Saboda haka, tallafawar hanya numfashi yana da mahimmanci don sauƙaƙe bayyanar cututtuka da kuma ceton rayuka kuma ya haɗa duk jiyya ta iska, iska mai saurin motsawa, samun iska daga na’ura, ya danganta ga tsananin cutar.
Marasa lafiya da bayyanar cutar hanyoyin numfashi mai tsanani dole ne a tallafa su da karin isaka (ECMO), wani ingantaccen dabarar bugun zuciya wanda aka yi amfani dashi don maganin cututtukan zuciya masu haɗari ko gazawar hanyoyin numfashi.
Bugu da kari, da daidaitawar ma'aunin electrolyte, rigakafin da lura da kamuwa da cuta da sakin jiki, da kuma kariya daga ayyukan gabobin jiki ma suna da matukar muhimmanci ga marasa lafiya na SARS-CoV-2.
An san cewa guguwar cytokine tana faruwa ne sakamakon wuce gona da iri na tsarin rigakafi a cikin marasa lafiyar SARS da MERS.
Guguwar Cytokine wani nau'i ne na yanayi amsar tsarin kumburi wanda aka gabatar ta hanyar jerin cytokines da suka hada da TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, da MCP-1.
Waɗannan cytokines tare da tantanin halita mai garkuwa su saki ɗimbin kwayoyi mara canzawa waɗanda sune babban dalilin ARDS da kuma gazawar gabobin jiki da yawa.
Danna rigakafi yana da muhimmanci a lura da guguwar cytokine, musamman a cikin majinyata masu rauni sosai.
Corticosteroids da tocilizumab, anti-IL6 monoclonal garkuwar jiki, an yi amfani dasu don magance guguwar cytokine.
Sauran jiyya danna rigakafi don guguwa ta cytokine sun hada da daidaitawa da amsawa kai tsaye na rigakafin tantanin halita T; toshewar IFN-γ, IL-1, da TNF; JAK hanawa; blinatumomab; mai danna alamar cytokine 4; da HDAC masu hanawa.
Maganin Steroids, kamar immunosuppressants, aka yi amfani da su sosai a cikin lura da SARS don rage tsananin lalacewa kumburi.
Duk da haka, shan steroids sosai ba su da fa'ida ga mummunan raunin huhu a cikin marasa lafiyar SARS da COVID-19.
Madadin haka, suna iya haifar da mummunar illa, musamman cututtukan osteonecrosis, da ke haifar da tasirin cutar.
Kodayake, gajerun darussan na corticosteroids a ƙarancin-zuwa-matsakaitan allurai an bada shawarar ayi amfani dasu da hankali don marasa lafiya COVID-19 marasa lafiya.
A lokacin rubutu, babu ingantaccen maganin rigakafi da aka tabbatar.
Duk da haka, badawa ta jijiya da remdesivir, wani nucleotide na analog, ana samun inganci a cikin marasa lafiyar COVID-19 na Amurka.
Remdesivir wata sabon maganin rigakafin ƙwayoyin cuta ne wanda Gidiyon ta kirkiro da farko don jiyyar cututtukan da cutar Ebola da Marlburg suka haifar.
Daga baya, sakatariya ya kuma nuna yiwuwar hana sauran kwayoyin cutar RNA guda da suka hada da kwayoyin cututtukar MERS da SARS.
Dangane da waɗannan, Gidiyon ya ba wa mahaɗin zuwa China don gudanar da gwaji guda biyu a kan mutane masu kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2, kuma ana sa ran samun sakamako sosai.
Bugu da ƙari, an ba da shawarar baricitinb, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir, da ribavirin a matsayin hanyoyin kwantar da hankalin marasa lafiya wanda ke da cutar hanyoyin numfashi mai tsanani.
Zawo, tashin zuciya, amai, lalacewar hanta, da sauran raunin azaba na iya faruwa bayan an haɗawar jinyar tare da lofinavir/ritonavir.
Hulɗawar waɗannan jiyya tare da wasu magunguna da aka yi amfani da su a cikin marasa lafiya ya kamata a sa ido sosai.
Plasma daga marasa lafiya da suka samu sauki da garkuwar jiki.
Tarin jini daga marasa lafiyar da suka murmure daga wata cuta mai yaduwa don yi wa wasu marasa lafiya da ke fama da wannan cuta ko kuma kare lafiyar mutane daga kamuwa da cutar yana da dogon tarihi.
Tabbas, mara lafiyar da aka dawo dasu galibi suna da babban matakin kariya daga kwayar cuta a cikin jinin su.
Garkuwar jiki sune rigakafi immunoglobulin (Ig) wanda aka samar daga B lymphocytes don yaƙar ƙwayoyin cuta da sauran abubuwa na ƙasashen waje kuma suna sane da kwayoyi na musamman a cikin cututtukan da ke cikin su.
Dangane da wannan, an karɓo plasma daga jinin gungun masu haƙuri waɗanda suka warke daga COVID-19 kuma an saka shi cikin marasa lafiya 10 mara lafiya sosai.
Alamar cutar su ta inganta cikin sa'o'i 24, tare da rage kumburi da rahusa da kuma inganta jijiyar oxygen a cikin jini.
Duk da haka, tabbatarwa da bayani wajibi ne don gabatar da hanyar don babban amfani kafin takamaiman hanyoyin kwantar da hankali ba su inganta ba.
Bugu da kari, da aka ba da tasirin warkewa, za a yi la’akari da wasu kasala da ke da alaƙa da plasma a hankali.
Alal misali, cututtukan rigakafi na iya wuce gona da iri kan hanyar kariya kuma suna haifar da sakin alamar alcytokine, wanda ke iya zama haɗarin rayuwa.
Taruwar garkuwar jiki cikin jini yawancin lokuta na ƙadan, kuma buƙatun plasma yana da yawa don kula da marasa lafiya da ke fama da rashin lafiya.
Yana da wuya a haɓaka da samar da takamaiman ƙwayoyin rigakafi cikin hanzari don yaƙi da annobar duniya.
Don haka, abu mafi mahimmanci ne kuma mai kyawu ne a kebe tantanin halittar jikin B (B cells) daga marassa lafiyar da suka warke kuma gano lambobin kwayar halitta wadanda ke hade da ingantattun garkuwar jiki ko duba garkuwa musamman a kan muhimman furotin na kwayan cutar.
