Asalin zoonotic na coronaviruses na mutum
Maye gurbi da kuma daidaitawa ne suka haifar da juyin halittun coronaviruses (CoVs) da wajen zaman su, har ma da mutane, zuwa dubban shekaru.
Kafin 2003, CoVs na mutum guda biyu (HCoVs) an san su don haifar da ciwo mara tsanani, kamar sanyi na yau da kullun.
Barkewar cuta mai saurin kamuwar manufanshi da alamar (SARS) da cutar manufanshi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) sun juya kuɗin don bayyana yadda ɓarkewar cutar HCoV zata iya zamawa.
Fitowar SARS-CoV-2 a tsakiyar ƙasar Sin a ƙarshen shekarar 2019 ya turo cuttutukar CoVs gaba kuma ya ba mu mamaki da cewa yana da sauƙin aikawa ga juna amma yawan ƙwayar cutar sun rage idan aka kwatanta da ‘yar uwarta SARS-CoV.
Cutar HCoV ana samun sa ne daga dabbobi kuma fahimtar tushen HcoVs taimaka gaya.
Galibin kwayoyin halittar HCoVs sun samo asali ne daga jemagu inda suka kasance ba masu cutarwa ba.
Ana sane da halittukan da ke rik'e wasu cututtukar HCoVs a tsakani suma.
Gano ainihin dabbobin da ke dauke da cutar zai taimaka kai tsaye wajen kare mutane daga cutar.
Bincikar mu’amalar mai dauke da cutar CoV da dabbobi watakila zai taimaka wajen gano yaduwar kwayoyin halittar cutar CoV a jikin mutane.
A cikin wannan bita, mun gabatar da wani bayyani game da ilimin data kasance game da HCoV guda bakwai, tare da mai da hankali kan tarihin gano su da yadda aka samo asalin zoonotic da kuma yada jinsunan halittar.
Muhimmin abu a nan shi ne, mu tantance banbanci tsakanin kwayar cutar HCoVs daga fahimtar yadda asalin kwayar cuta take rikada da kuma kwayoyin halitta suke rikida daga asalin tushensu.
Cutar CoV da ake fama da ita a 2019 mai suna (COVID-19) wacce annoba ce, an yi bayani game da ita a nan.
Bugu da ƙari, an jaddada yadda abunda ake buƙata domin ƙwayar cutar ta samu nasarar masauka wanda ke sauyawa kuma anlmm jaddada sakamakon yadda juyin halittar kwayar cutar ke tsananta cutar.
Kwayoyin cutar Corona (CoVs) sun kasance dangin Coronaviridae, wanda ya hada da tabbatacciyar rukunin kwayoyin cututtukan RNA mai zare daya.
Wadannan kwayoyin cututtukan sun kunsar da babban ma’adanin kwayar halittar kamaceceniya na RNA daga 26 zuwa 32 nasu, dalilin da yasa ake kiransu “CoVs” wanda ake iya gani a tabarau na microscope.
A gine dai, CoVs suna da kwayoyin halittar da ba a rarrabe su ba wanda ke da shiri kamar haka.
Kimanin kashi biyu bisa uku na halittar suna dauke da manyan furanni masu budewa biyu (ORF1a da ORF1b), wadanda ake fassara su cikin pp1a da pp1ab kwafin polyproteins.
Ana ƙara aiwatar da polyproteins don samar da furotin 16 waɗanda ba na tsari ba, waɗanda aka tsara nsp1~16.
Sauran bangaren tushen halittar mai dauke da ORFs domin abu mai gina jiki kamar su, nau‘in spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) and nucleoprotein (N).
Yawancin nau'ikan sinadaran zuriya, su ma ana lulluɓe su da wasu zuriyoyin CoVs daban.
Dangane da bambanci a cikin jerin abubuwan gina jiki, ana rarraba CoVs zuwa abubuwa huɗu (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV da delta-CoV), tsakanin abin da beta-CoV ya ƙunshi yawancin HCoVs kuma an rarrabasu cikin kashi huɗu (A, B, C da D).
Hujjojin halittun dabbobi sun nuna cewa jemagu da dabbobin suna aiki a matsayin tushen asalin yawancin alpha-CoVs da beta-CoVs, yayin da tsuntsaye sune babban tafki na gamma-CoVs da delta-CoVs
Shekaru dubbai yanzu, CoVs sun shawo kan shingen jinsuna kuma wasu sun fito a matsayin mahimman ƙwayoyin cuta na mutane.
Har ya zuwa yau din nan, an san cututtukan na CoVs (HCoVs) nau’i bakwai ne a jikin dan adam.
Daga cikinsu HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 sune alpha-CoVs.
Sauran beta-CoV guda biyar sun hada da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, cutar hanyoyin numfashi mai tsanani na coronavirus (SARS-CoV), cutar numfashi na gefen larabawa coronavirus (MERS-CoV) da SARS-CoV-2.
Cututtukan HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43 da HCoV-HKU1 da kuma HCoV-NL63 galibi su kan haifar da alamomin cuta marasa karfi sosai kamar mura da ko kuma gudawa.
Saɓanin haka, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da subuwar cutar SARS-CoV-2 da aka gano sune cututtuka masu mafi yaɗuwa da ke haifar da mummunan rauni na jijiyoyin jiki a marasa lafiya tare da babbar damar haɓaka ciwo mai rauni na rashin damuwa na jiki (ARDS) da bayyananniyar cututtuka.
Nau'in HCoV-229E na farko, B814, ya kasance mai rabuwa daga fitowar hancin marasa lafiya masu fama da murar yau da kullum a tsakiyar shekarun 1960.
Tun daga lokacin, ake ta samun ilimi kan HCoV-229E da kuma HCoV-OC43, ta hanyar zurfafa nazarin alamun cutar.
Tabbas, an yarda da ra'ayin cewa kamuwa da cutar HCoVs gaba daya ba shi da matsala har sai fashewar SARS.
Barkewar cutar SARS da ta faru a cikin shekarar 2003, shi ne ɗaya mafi munin balaguro a cikin tarihin na yanzu, da ya kamu da mutane sama da 8,000 da ke cikin mummunan yanayin mutuwar kusan kashi 10%.
Shekaru goma bayan haka, barkewar cutar numfashi na gefen larabawa wato Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS) ya haifar da annoba na yau da kullum a Kasashen Larabawa tare da yaduwa zuwa sauran sassan duniya.
Sabuwar cutar HCoV ta shekarar 2019 (2019-nCoV), wanda daga baya aka sake masa suna SARS-CoV-2, shine wakili na abubuwanda ke faruwa na ci gaba da cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), wanda ya yi sanadiyar rayuka sama da 3,120 kuma ya kamu da mutane sama da dubu 91,000 a cikin watan Maris 3, 2020.
Ƙararrawar tana ta kaɗawa kuma dole duniya ta shirya akan annobar cutar SARS-CoV-2 da ke zuwa.
Dukkanin HCoV guda bakwai suna da asalin fitowa daga dabbobi kamar su jemagu, beraye ko dabbobin gida.
Bayanan shaida da yawa suna tallafawa asalin juyin halittar dukkanin HCoVs daga jemagu, inda ƙwayoyin cuta suke dacewa da kyau kuma ba masu bada ciwon ba ne amma na nuna babban bambancin kwayoyin halita.
COVID-19 annobar cutar ta gabatar da babban kalubale na likita, kimiyya, zamantakewa da halin kirki ga kasar Sin da duniya.
Binciken asalin dabbobin da suka janyo HCoVs yana ba da tsarin fahimtar tarihin halitta, ƙarfin tuƙi da abubuwan da ke hana ƙetare na tsallen jinsin.
Wannan na iya jagorantar ko sauƙaƙe bincika tafkin, matsakaici da haɓaka rundunar garken dabbobi (s) na SARS-CoV-2, tare da mahimmancin tasiri cikin karewar abin da ke dawowa nan gaba.
A cikin wannan bitar, mun gabatar da wani taƙaitaccen bayani game da asalin cututtukar dabbobi (zoonotic), watsawarsu tsakanin nau’in jinsun kansu da gine-ginen HCoVs.
Musamman ma, muna karin haske da bayani kan tushen kwayoyin cutar HCoVs ba wai sun samo asali ne daga kwayoyin halittar da basa haifar da cuta a jiki bayan sun shiga jikin wani na daban.
Mun kuma sake nazarin yanayin cigaban HCoV wanda karuwa a watsawa sau da yawa yana zuwa tare da raguwa a cikin mai bada kwayar cutan.
Ana bayanin sakamakon da barkewar ita ma cutar SARS-CoV-2 a nan.
An san CoV na dabbobi tun ƙarshen shekarun 1930.
Kafin farkon warewar iri B814 na HCoV-229E daga zubar hancin wanda ya kamu da mura na yau da kullun, an ware CoVs a dabbobi daban-daban wanda suka kamu da cutar kamar tolotolo, ɓera, shanu, alade, kule da kare.
A shekara ashirin da suka gabata, an gano kwayoyin cuatr dangin HCoVs.
Takaitaccen tarihin gano cutar HCoV a jerin jadawalin farko na wannana teburi (Tebur 1) zai zama mai gamsarawa tare da bayar da cikakken bayani a kai.
Rashin HCoV-229E na farko ya kasance a kebe daga cutar hanyar numfashi na marasa lafiya da cutar sama hanyar numfashi a shekarar 1966, daga baya ya sami karbuwa girma cikin layin tantanin halitar huhu WI-38.
Marasa lafiya waɗanda ke kamuwa da HCoV-229E da aka gabatar tare da alamun sanyi na yau da kullun, gami da ciwon kai, atishawa, rashin jin dadi, zazzabi da ciwon-makogwaro, da zazzabi da tari da aka gani cikin damu’oin kashi 10~20%.
Daga baya a shekarar 1967, an ware HCoV-OC43 daga hanyar binciken ‘organ culture’ da kuma hanyar renon cuta (serial passage) da zai biyo a kwakwalwar jariran ɓeraye.
Siffofin asibiti na kamuwa da HCoV-OC43 suna kama da waɗanda HCoV-229E ke haifar, waɗanda ke alammar nuna bambanci daga kamuwa da wasu cututtukan ƙwayoyin cuta kamar mura da ƙwayoyin cuta da kuma rhinoviruses.
Dukansu HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43 na yaɗuwa a duk faɗin duniya, kuma galibi suna watsawa a lokacin bazara, a cikin yanayi marasa dumi ko sanyi.
Yawanci dai, lokacin yaɗuwar waɗannan ƙwayoyin cututtuka guda biyu shi ne ƙasa da mako ɗaya, hakan na biye da sa rashin lafiyan kusan makonai 2.
Dangane da binciken masu ba da agaji na ɗan adam, mutane masu lafiya waɗanda suka kamu da cutar HCoV-229E sun kamu da sanyi na yau da kullun.
Kalilan marasa lafiya wadan da garkuwar jikin sub ba karfi ne ke nuna tsananin kamuwa hanyar manufanshi da cuta.
"SARS, wanda kuma aka sani da ""kwayar cutar huhu"", shine farkon bayanan da aka samu na cutar HCoV-da ke haifar da ƙwayar cuta a cikin tarihin ɗan adam kuma wakili na etiological shine SARS-CoV, HCoV na uku da aka gano."
Ana iya gano kamuwar SARS ta farko zuwa karshen 2002 a lardin Guangdong na kasar Sin.
Cutar ta SARS ta haifar da mutane 8,096 da aka ruwaito sun kamu da asarar rayuka 774, sun bazu cikin kasashe da nahiyoyi da yawa.
Ban da manyan gwaraza, an kiyasta hakan kowane damuwa na iya ba da kusan damu’oi biyu na, tare da lokacin shiryawa na kwanaki 4 zuwa 7 da gangar jikin kwayar cutar ta bayyana a ranar 10 ta rashin lafiya.
Marasa lafiya waɗanda ke kamuwa da SARS-CoV da farko suna kasancewa tare da myalgia, ciwon kai, zazzabi, zazzabin cizon sauro da tsananin sanyi, biyo bayan dyspnea, tari da matsananciyar damuwa kamar bayyanar cututtuka.
Lymphopenia, gwajin aikin hanta, da haɓaka sinadarin creatine kinase abubuwa ne na gama-gari wurin gwaji na SARS.
Diffuse alveolar damage (lalacewar huhu), epithelial cell proliferation (yaɗuwar ƙwayoyin halittar kan jiki), kuma an gano karuwar macrophages (ƙwayoyin halittar farin jini) a cikin marasa lafiyar SARS.
Aƙalla kashi 20-30% na marasa lafiya daga baya suna buƙatar kulawa mai zurfi da samun iska.
Bayan hanyar numfashi ta ƙasa, gabobin cikin jiki da yawa, ciki har da na ciki, hanta da koda na iya kamuwa da cutar a cikin waɗannan mummunan yanayin cutar, yawanci tare da hadarin cytokine, wanda kan iya kashewa musamman ga marasa lafiya marasa kariyar lafiya.
An fara ware kwayar cutar ne daga tarin kwayoyin cutar huhu na wani dan uwan mai cutar Ebola wanda ya tafi Hong Kong daga Guangzhou.
Tun lokacin kuma ake ta kokarin nazari kan cutar HCoV.
HCoV-NL63 an ware shi daga wani yaro dan watanni 7 daga Netherlands a ƙarshen 2004.
An samo shi ne da farko a cikin yara ƙanana, tsofaffi da marasa lafiyan mara garkuwa wato immunocompromised da cutan numfashi.
Gabatar coryza, conjunctivitis, zazzabi, da mashako ya zama ruwan dare a cikin cutar da HCoV-NL63 ta haifar.
Wani bincike mai zaman kansa ya bayyana warewar cutar guda daga samfurin hanci daga wani yaro dan watanni 8 da ke fama da ciwon huhu a Netherlands.
Ko da yake a gano ta ne a kasar Netherlands, amma tabbas dai an yada ta a duniya.
An yi kiyasin cewa kwayoyin halittar HCoV-NL63 sune keda alhakin akalla kashi 4.7 na cututtukan numfashi, kuma yana ganiyarsa a daidai shigar lokacin bazara da kaka da kuma hunturu.
HCoV-NL63 yana da alaƙar da cutar kumburin beli mai toshewa, wanda kuma aka sani da croup.
A shekara daya ce, cutar HCoV-HKU1 aka fara gano ta daga wani dattijo mai shekara 71 wanda aka garzaya da shi asibiti sakamakon cutar shakewar numfashi ta pneumonia da kuma cutar huhu a birnin Hong Kong.
Bayan ciwon huhu da na hanyoyin huhu wadanda al'umma ke samu, an ruwaito cewa HCoV-HKU1 yana da alaƙa da matsanancin rashin lafiyar asma.
Kama da HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 an samu a duk duniya, suna haifar da karamin cutan manufanci.
Duk waɗannan HCoVs huɗu da al'umma suka samu wurin zama a mutane kuma galibi ba su da ikon canzawa don haifar da kwayoyin cututtuka sosai, kodayake hatsarori sun faru ne saboda dalilai da ba a san su ba kamar yadda a cikin mafi yawan yanayi mai kama da HCoV-NL63, wanda a kwanan nan aka ba da rahoton cewa yana haifar da cuta kasa hanyar numfashi mai tsanani a China.
Gabaɗaya, lokacin da waɗannan HCoVs suka sami damar iya watsuwa yadda yakamata kuma su riƙe kansu gabaɗaya cikin ɗan-adam, su kuma suna zama ƙasa da ɓarna ko kuma cutarwa.
An fara ware MERS-CoV ne a cikin 2012 a cikin huhu na wani mara lafiya mai shekaru 60 wanda ya kamu da matsananciyar cutar huhu da gazawar koda a Saudiya.
Ganin cewa mafi yawan kwayoyin da aka tabbatar da asali sun fito ne daga Gabas ta Tsakiya, an bayar da rahoton yaduwa ta biyu na gaba zuwa makusantan sadarwa a kasashe daban-daban na Turai da Tunusiya.
Wani fashewa ta sakandare ya faru a Koriya ta Kudu a cikin 2015 tare da tabbatarwan mutane 186 da cutar.
Bayyanannin asibiti na MERS sun yi kama da na SARS, wanda ke nunawa da mummunan ciwon huhu.
Sai dai ba kamar cutar SARS ba, da dama daga cikin majinyatan murar ta MERS sun kuma gamu da matsalar ciwon koda, wanda ya zama babban dalili da ya sa banbanta cuatr ta MERS da kuma kwayoyin cututtukan da ke samuwa daga HCoV.
Fiye da kashi 30% na marasa lafiya da ke tare da alamun gastrointestinal, kamar gudawa da amai.
Ya zuwa ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kamuwa sama da 2500 da aka tabbatar a dakin gwaje-gwaje sun kasance tare da mutuwar kasha 34.4 cikin dari, wadda ya sa MERS-CoV ta zama daya daga cikin cututtukan da ke lalata mutane sosai da aka taba samu.
Daidai lokacin tsakiyar watan Disamban 2019, an samu wasu marasa lafiya masu fama da shakewar numfashi ko pneumonia da a lokacin aka yi tunanin tana kama da cutar SARS-CoV-2 wandanda aka gano a birnin Wuhan, lardin Hubei, da ke kasar China.
Hukumar Kiwon Lafiya ta Duniya ta ba da sanarwar ci gaban barkewar cuta kasan hanyar manufanci wanda haifar da SARS-CoV-2 da shi wanda ya zama babban kalubale ga lafiyar Jama'a na Kasa da Kasa kuma ya sanya sunan cutar COVID-19.
Ya zuwa ranar 3 ga watan Maris, 2020, as tabbatar da mutane masu kamuwa 90,053 a duniya, tare da yawan mutuwa saboda kamuwa wanda ya kai kashi 3.4%..
Musamman ma, yawan wadanda suka mutu daga cutar a Hubei, China ya kai kashi 4.2 cikin dari, alhali wanda yake waje da can kashi 1.2 cikin dari ne.
SARS-CoV-2 yana haifar da tsananin cutan numfashi kamar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, an gabatar da su azaman zazzabi, tari da dyspnea.
Ana kuma ganin cutar gudawa a wasu marassa lafiyan.
Cutar huhu na ɗaya daga cikin alamun bayyanar cututtuka kuma yana iya ci gaba cikin hanzari zuwa ciwo mai wahala na manumfashi.
Kodayake SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 suna da kama sosai saboda halayyar ƙwayoyin nucleotide na kasha 82%, suna curewa cikin rassa daban-daban a cikin bishiyar kwayoyin halittar.
Idan aka kwatanta da SARS-CoV wadda yake da babban adadin maye gurbi, adadin maye gurbi na SARS-CoV-2 yana kasa sosai, wadda ke nuna girman matakin karbuwa ga mutane.
Wani mai nuna alamar kamu da SARS-CoV-2 wanda aka bada rahoton iya ba da gudummawa ga saurin yaduwa a duniya.
Kwatantawa da kuma musanya SARS-CoV-2 tare da sauran HCoV guda shida suna nuna kamanni da bambance-bambance masu babban mahimmanci.
Na farko dai, lokacin kyankyasar cutar da kuma yadda cutar ta HCoV ke samuwa na kama da juna.
A wannan batun, SARS-CoV-2 yana bin yanayin gaba ɗaya na sauran HCoV guda shida.
Na biyu shi ne zafin alamun cutar COVID-19 ya dogara ne tsakanin cutar SARS-CoV da kuma sauran ire-irensu guda hudu: HCoVs (i.e. HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 and HCoV-NL63).
A bangare guda, kamuwa da cuta SARS-CoV-2 yana nuna fasali waɗanda aka fi ganinsu yayin kamuwa da cutar HCoVs, da al'umma ke samu, gami da gabatar da marasa takamaiman, mai saukin kai ko ma babu alamun su.
A gefe guda, ana iya ganin ƙaramin kashin tsananin kamuwa da COVID-19 kamar yadda ake ganin ta a kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV, duk da haka kashin yana da karanci.
Na uku, watsuwar SARS-CoV-2 kuma yana nuna alamun halayen ban sha'awa na samun HCoVs da al'umma kan yi da na SARS-CoV.
A bangare guda, bazuwar SARS-CoV-2 ya yi daidai da na HCoVs wanda al'umma suka samu.
A wata gefe guda, ya rage don tabbatar da ko yiwuwar rikicewar SARS-CoV-2 ya ragu bayan bayanan wurare a cikin mutane kamar yadda yake a yanayin SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV.
A ƙarshe, daidai da sauran HCoVs, SARS-CoV-2 za'a iya gano su a cikin samfuran fecal.
Nazarin cewa ko cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta yadu ta hanyar kashin da ya shiga ta baki ya taka muhimmiyar rawa wajen yada cutar SARS-CoV zai zama sai nan gaba za a tabbatar da haka a binciken da za a yi.
Hakanan yana da matukar sha'awar ganin ko SARS-CoV-2 na iya bayyanar da yanayi kamar yadda al'amuran al'umma suka samu HCoVs.
Koyaya, siffofin SARS-CoV-2 gami da wucewa, pathogenicity da ci gaba mai yadawa bayan wurare a cikin mutane zasu zama masu tasiri akan ƙarshen ƙaddarar barkewar COVID-19.
Dukkanin al'ummomin guda huɗu sun samo HCoVs waɗanda ke haifar da bayyanar cututtuka masu alaƙa sun daidaita ga mutane.
Ta wata hanyar, zai iya zama gaskiya ne cewa 'yan Adam sun daidaita da waɗannan HCoVs huɗu.
Ta wata hanyar, duka biyun zasu iya kasancewa daga rayuwar tsoffin anoban HCoV.
HCoVs waɗanda ke haifar da mummunan cututtuka a cikin mutane da mutane waɗanda suka kamu da mummunan cututtukan HCoV an kawar dasu.
Domin wannan ya faru, HCoVs na bukatar su rubanya a cikin mutane zuwa isasshen mataki don ba da damar tattaruwar maye gurbi da zai ci galabar dalilan ƙuntatawa na mafaka.
Ta wannan hanyar, tsawon lokacin fashewa da SARS-CoV-2 ya ci gaba kuma mutane da yawa suna cutar dashi, mafi girma damar cewa zai cikakken daidaita da ga mutane.
Idan har ta samu gindin zama sosai, yaduwarta tsakanin mutum zuwa mutum zai zama da matukar wahala ta hanyar killacewa ko kuma sauran matakan kare bazuwar cuta.
Shekaru da yawa, al'umma huɗu sun samo CoVs suna kewayawa cikin yawan mutane, yana haifar da sanyin mura cikin kwararun masun garkuwa.
Wadannan kwayoyin cutar basa bukatar zama a jikin mutum ko dabba.
Sabanin haka, SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV masu sanya cuta ba su daidaita da mutane ba da kyau kuma yaduwarsu a mutane ba za a iya cigaba da shi ba.
Suna da bukatar ci gaba da rayuwa a jikin dabbobin da ke dauke da su domin su sami damar shiga jikin mutane ta hanyar mutum guda ko fiye da samo ta daga dabbobin.
Cutar SARS-CoV-2 tana da kamanni irin na cutar SARS-CoV/MERS-CoV da kuma sauran masu dauke da nau’in cutar HCoVs.
Wannan abu ne da za'a iya yaduwa sosai kamar kamuwar HCOVs a cikin al'umma, aƙalla a lokacin da muke a ciki.
Duk da haka, ya fi zaman mai daukar kwayar cuta fiye da al’uma da aka sami HCoVs kuma ƙasa da mai daukar kwayar cutan fiye da SARS-CoV ko MERS-CoV.
Ya rage a gani ko zai iya dacewa da mutane sosai kuma ya kewaya cikin mutane ba tare da wurin ajiya ba ko mafaka ta tsakiya a jikin dabbobi.
Kafin tattauna asalin dabbobin dabbobi na HCoVs, zai taimaka mana sosai mu tattauna kan ma’anoni da halayen juyin halitta, na halitta, tafki, matsakaici da haɓaka mafakar HCoVs.
Dabba da ta zama wata mafaka ta juyin halitta ta HCoV idan ta tanadi asalin magabata mai kusanci wadda suke babban kama ta haɗin dangantaka a matakin jerin nucleotide.
Kwayar cutar ta asali galibi ana rayuwa da ita kuma bata zama illa ga inda dama take rayuwa.
Hakanan, mai yin tafki mai tashar jiragen ruwa HCoV yana ci gaba kuma tsawon lokaci.
A dukkan halayen, masu rukunin suna kamuwa da cuta ta dabi'a kuma sune ainihin rukunin HCoV ko ƙwayar mahaifa.
Sabanin haka, idan sabon HCoV ya gabatar da sabon matsakaici a gabanin ko a kusa da gabatarwar sa ga mutane, ba a daidaita shi da sabon mai masaukin ba kuma yawanci shine pathogenic.
Wannan da kwayar cutar ta samu gindin zama jikinsa, zai iya zama tushen da cutar da za ta shafa kuma ya taka muhimmiyar rawa wajen bai wa kwayar cutar damar ta hayayyafa inda za ta iya harbin dan adam daga nan.
HCoV na iya yin gwajin cutar mutu-karshen idan har ba zai iya ci gaba da yada ta ba a cikin matsakaiciyar mai watsa shiri.
Sai dai wani abin da zai zama wanda ya saba da hakan, cutar HCoVs kan iya rayuwa jikin wani abu na daban kuma ya iya haifar da illar gaske da za ta dauki lokaci gabanin bayyanarta.
A nan kuma, wanda cutar ta kasance a jikinsa na karshe to zai zama wanda ainihin inda cutar ta samo asali tun da farko.
Bayanan cututtukan dabbobi sun bayyana bita da kullun cewa yanayin binciken SARS yana da tarihin hulɗa tare da dabbobin wasa.
