Wannan ya tallafawa kai tsaye ta hanyar cewa ba a sake samun ƙarin rahoton SARS ba bayan kashe duk wasu dabbobin Sivets cikin kasuwannin.
Duk da haka, an ba da rahoton cewa dabban itacen giginya wato civets daga cikin daji ko gonaki ba tare da fuskantar kasuwannin dabbobi masu rai ba sun kasance da cutar SARS-CoV ba, wadda ke nunar da cewa civets masu rufaffen tafi watakila kawai su zama mafakar tsakiya mai fadadawa ga SARS-CoV amma ba mafakan sa ba.
Musamman ma, tunda kashi 80% na dabbobi daban-daban a cikin kasuwanni a Guangzhou suna da rigakafin SARS-CoV da yiwuwar cewa yawancin nau'in kananan dabbobi masu shayarwa suma zasu iya zama matsakaicin fadada rundunonin SARS-CoV ba za'a iya cire su ba.
Dukkanin wadannan sun kasance inda cutar SARS-CoV take mutuwa a jikinsu.
Bincike mai zuwa don rundunar dabba ta SARS-CoV sun nuna wata jemage mai zaman kusa da CoV da ake kira SARS-Jemagen Rhinolophus CoV HKU3 (SARSr-Rh-JemageCoV HKU3), wanda yake a cikin jikunan dawakai na kasar Sin.
Wadannan jemagun suna dauke da kwayoyin halitta masu maganin SARS-CoV da kwayoyin tsuhen halitta masu ajin SARSr-Rh-BatCoV HKU3.
Wannan da sauran CoVs na jemagu suna da nasaba kashi 88-92% ta jerin kwayoyin nucleotide tare da SARS-CoV.
Wadannan karatuttukan sun aza harsasai ga sabuwar manufar da jemagu ke karbar bakuncin cututtukan dan adam.
Yawancin CoVs (SL-CoVs) masu kama da SARS an kuma gano su daga jemagu, amma babu wani idan ba guda kawai da aka tsara WIV1 da za a iya warewa a zaman ƙwayar cuta mai rai.
Kayan mutum wanda yake canza enzyme 2 (ACE2) an san shi mai karɓar SARS-CoV.
Kwayar WIV1 da aka samo daga kashin jemagu an yi amfani da shi ne a jemagen da kyanwa da kuma ACE2 na mutum a matsayin masu karbar kwayar halittar.
Abin ban sha'awa, fama da cutar SARS wanda suna samun sauki sun iya wargazawar WIV1.
Har zuwa yau, WIV1 tana wakiltar asalin magabata na SARS-CoV a cikin jemage, yana kamanni mataki na 95% nucleotide jerin homology.
Duk da haka, akwai babban tsarin alaƙa tsakanin waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta guda biyu, gabaɗaya an yi imanin cewa WIV1 ba ƙwayar cuta ce ta iyaye na nan take na SARS-CoV kuma jemagu ba shine reshe na kai tsaye na SARS-CoV ba.
Binciken ƙwayar Phylogenetic ta mahaɗar MERS-CoV zuwa rukuni guda na Jemage CoV-HKU4 da baton CoV-HKU5.
CoV-HKU4 na jemage da MERS-CoV suna yin amfani da mai karɓa guda, da dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4), don shigowar ƙwayar cutar virus.
Jerin kwayoyin halittar RNA-dependent da kuma na miyau RNA suna daga cutar MERS-CoV suna kama ne da jemagun da ake gani a nahiyar Turai da kuma Afirka.
Har ya zuwa maganan nan da muke yanzu, babu wata alamar kwayar cutar MERS-CoV da take rayuwa a jikin jemagun daji.
Kwayar cutar MERS-CoV da kuma wacce tafi kama da ita ta jemage mai suna CoV-HKU25 suna da nasaba ta kashi 87% a kwayoyin halittarsu masu kamanceceniya da juna.
Don haka jemagu watakila ba sune ke dauke da kwayar cutar MERS-CoV.
A gefe guda, bincike a Gabas ta Tsakiya ya nuna cewa raƙuman masu tozo guda suna da matsalar virus ga ƙwayoyin magance ƙwayoyin cuta na MERS-CoV, daidai da raƙuman masu asalin daga gabas ta Tsakiya wadanda ke cikin ƙasashen Afirka da yawa.
MERS-CoV mai raye daidai ne da cutar da aka samu a cikin mutane an ware ta daga kwarfatar hanci na raƙuman maso tozo guda, wanda ke cigaba da nuna cewa rakuma suna aiki a matsayin taskar mafaka ta MERS-CoV.
Hakanan abin lura ne cewa yawancin alamu masu saukin kai amma an lura da zubar da kwayar cutar a cikin raƙuma na gwaji yayin kamuwa da MERS-CoV.
Musamman, raƙuma masu kamuwa da cuta suna zubar da ƙwayoyin cuta ba kawai ta hanyar numfashi ba amma har ma ta hanyar fecal-na baka, wanda kuma shine babban hanyar cutar zubar da kwari daga jemagu.
Koyaya, tambayoyi har yanzu suna kasancewa tunda masu kamuwa da MERS su da yawa sun tabbatar da cewa ba su da tarihin hulɗa da raƙuma kafin farawa samun alamar cuta, wanda ake dangantawa watsuwa tskanin mutum-zuwa-mutum ko ta hanyoyi da ba a sani ba wadanda suka shafi nau'in dabbobi da ba a gano su ba wadanda suke dauke da MERS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 na raba kashi 96.2% na nucleotide homology tare da wata bature CoV RaTG13 da aka ware daga jemagun affinis Rhinolophus.
Kamar yadda ya faru da SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, rarrabewa tsakanin SARS-CoV-2 da RaTG13 ya yi girma da yawa don sanya dangantakar iyaye.
Abin nufi shine, jemagu bazai kasance mai masaukin na kai tsaye na SARS-CoV-2 ba sai dai idan an samo kusan kwatankwacin batutuwan CoVs masu zuwa nan gaba.
Wataƙila, rundunan dabbobi masu matsakaici na SARS-CoV-2 ya kamata ya kasance cikin nau'in namun daji da aka sayar kuma an kashe shi a Kasuwar sayar da abincin teku, wanda yawancin farkon damuwar COVID-19 suke da alaƙa, alamu ne na yiwuwar watsawar cutan daga dabbobi-zuwa-mutum.
Yawancin binciken da aka yi kwanan nan dangane da jerin hanyoyin metagenomic sun nunar da wasu ƙananan dabbobi masu shayarwa dake haɗarin bata, wadanda aka sani da pangolins (Manis javanica) suna iya kasancewa masu dauke da magabata beta-CoVs wanda ya dangantaka da SARS-CoV-2.
Wadannan sabbin kwayoyin genome na pangolin CoV suna hadakar kwayoyin genomes 85-92% na tsarin kwayoyin nucleotide homology tare da SARS-CoV-2.
Ko yaya, suna da alaƙa da RaTG13 da kusan kasha 90 bisa dari Asali a matakin nucleotide.
Suna tattaruwa cikin sassan biyu na SARS-CoV-2-kamar ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin bishiyar phylogenetic, ɗayan wanda ya raba yanki mai ɗaukar nauyi mai rikodin mai karɓa (RBD) tare da SARS-CoV-2, tare da 97.4% shaidar asalin jerin amino asid.
Ko yaya dai, yawan maye gurbi RBDs na SARS-CoVs-2 da RaTG13 su na daban-daban kusan sau miliyan ne fiye da wanda ke daukar su.
Wani binciken da ya gabata a kan pangolins masu cutuka shi ma ya ba da labarin gano alamun kwayar cutar virus daga samfuran huhu, wanda ya yi kama da masu alaƙa da SARS-CoV-2.
Wannan binciken ya karɓi hanyoyi daban-daban na haɗuwa da kundin jagora don samar da jerin abubuwan genome wanda ya ƙunshi kimanin kashi 86.3% na cikakkiyar ƙwayoyin cuta ta genome.
Ba za mu kawar da yiwuwar cewa dabbar pangolin din tana daga cikin dabbobin da suke dauke da kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Duk da haka, a halin yanzu babu wata shaida a cikin goyon bayan asalin pangolin kai tsaye na SARS-CoV-2 saboda rarrabewar jerin tsakanin SARS-CoV-2 da pangolin hadedeyar-SARS-CoV-2 da beta-CoVs.
Kari akan haka, nisan da ke tsakanin SARS-CoV-2 da RaTG13 ya fi guntu fiye da wancan tsakanin SARS-CoV-2 da pangolin SARS-CoV-2 masu hade da beta-CoVs.
Rikidar cutar SARS-CoV-2 a jikin jemagu da kuma dabbobin pangolin da ma sauransu ya zama wani abi da za a kafa hujja kansa.
Ganin cewa mafi girman jerin kwayoyin an samo cikin RBDs tsakanin SARS-CoV-2 da pangolin, SARS-CoV-2-beta-CoVs, beta-CoVs masu alaka da SARS-CoV-2 da RaTG13 suna kama mafi girma a jerin kwayoyin halittar jini.
Abun hasashe ne babba cewa girman matsayin dake kamance tsakanin RBDs na pangolin SARS-CoV-2-beta-CoV-beta da SARS-CoV-2 ana haifar da shi ne ta hanyar juyin halitta wanda yake rikidewa.
Neman shawara ya dace da sake hadewa tsakanin SARS-CoV-2 da aka hada da beta-CoV da RaTG13 a cikin dabbobin daji na uku.
A matsayin ƙarfin tuki a cikin juyin halitta, sake haɗa abubuwa da ke yaɗuwa sosai tsakanin beta-CoVs.
Har yanzu masu yanke hukunci suna kan asalin SARS-CoV-2 na zoonotic.
Idan ka cire batun rikidar kwayar cutar HcoVs data samo asali daga jikin dabbobi an kuma nazarci na’ukan HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43 da HCoV-NL63 da HCoV-HKU1.
Shaidar ilimin halittun dabbobi ya nuna cewa duka HCoV-NL63 da HCoV-229E za su iya samo asali ne daga jemage CoVs, yayin da aka sami ƙwayoyin cuta na iyaye na HCoV-OC43 da HCoV-HKU1 a cikin beraye.
An ba da rahoton cewa wata CoV ta jemage da ake kira ARCoV.2 (Appalachian Ridge CoV) wacce aka gano a jemage mai kala uku a Arewacin Amurka ta sami dangantaka mai kusanci da HCoV-NL63.
A wata gefe guda, HCoV-229E yana da alaƙar alaƙa da wani jigon CoV, ana kiran shi Hipposideros / GhanaKwam / 19/2008, wanda aka gano a Gana, yayin da kuma ana zargin raƙumin a matsayin mai ba da taimakon sa.
Don ba da haske, ilimin zamani game da asalin dabbobi na sananniyar HCoVs an taƙaita su a cikin Hoto na 1 da Tebur 2.
Nazarin Phylogenetic ya ba da hujja ga abubuwan da suka faru na watsa abubuwan HCoV a cikin tarihin.
Lokacin da HCoV-OC43 ya haɗu da jinsin don cutar da mutane daga dabbobin gida a shekarar 1890, an yi rikodin annoba ta numfashi.
Tarihin yaduwar cutar HCoV-229E ba wani karin haske sosai a kansa.
An gano kwayar cutar daga jemage CoVs wacce ta yi kama sosai da cutar HCoV-229E.
Tsakanin su akwai alpha mai suna 'alpaca-CoV.
Akwai hujjoji da dama da suke nuna cewa cutar ta yadu ne daga jemagu kai tsaye zuwa jikin dan adam.
Da farko, mutane amma ba almasas ba zasu iya hulɗa da jemagu a cikin raba kimiyyar muhalli.
Maimakon haka, mutane suna kusanci da alpacas.
Na biyu, HCoV-229E mai hade da batutuwan al-CoVs suna da bambanci kuma marasa tsari a cikin jemagu, alhali kuwa Alpha-CoV ya haifar da barkewar cutar ta hanu a cikin dabbobi masu kamuwa.
A ƙarshe, ba a sami alpaca alpha-CoV ba a cikin dabbobin feral.
Don haka, baza a kawar da tunanin yiyuwar cutar HCoV-229E ta samo asali ne daga kwayoyin halittar CoV daga dan jikin dan adam.
Hakika, jemagu sune tushen kai tsaye na ƙwayoyin cuta na mutum wanda ya haɗa da kwayar cutar rabies, ƙwayar cutar Ebola, ƙwayar cutar Nipah da ƙwayar cutar Hendra.
Don haka ba abin mamaki bane cewa jemagu na iya yada HCoV-229E ga mutane kai tsaye.
A wata hanya, yayin da alpha-CoVs suna aiki ne a matsayin hanyar samar da hanyar HCoV-229E, alpacas da raƙuman ruwa na iya zama matsakaiciyar runduna waɗanda ke aika ƙwayoyin cuta ga mutane, daidai kamar yadda yake a cikin yanayin MERS-CoV.
MERS-CoV ya zama wani kyakkyawan misali game da watsa sadarwa daga jemage zuwa raƙuman dabbobi da kuma raƙumi zuwa ga mutane.
Asalin juyin halitta na MERS-CoV daga jemagu an san shi a farkon ganowarsa kuma ya sami ƙarfafuwa sakamakon binciken da ya biyo baya.
A fili take cewa jemagu sune matattarar da ke dauke da cututtukan da za su iya yada su daga dabbobi zuwa mutane.
Dogon lokaci, dauloli masu cike da tarin yawa, kusanci da zamantakewa da kuma karfin ƙarfi don tashi duka yanayi ne da ya dace da jemage don zama kyakkyawan 'mai yada kwayoyin cutar.
A wata gefe guda, MERS-CoV an gabatar dashi ga raƙuman dromedary shekaru da yawa.
Ya dace da waɗannan raƙuma waɗanda suka juya daga matsakaici mai ban sha'awa zuwa barikin mai tsaro da na ɗabi'a na dabi'a.
MERS-CoV yana haifar da ciwo mai laushi kuma yana riƙe da ƙarancin maye gurbi a cikin waɗannan dabbobi.
Bazuwarta zuwa mutane ya faru haka kwatsam kmua mutane sune inda cutar MERS-CoV ba za ta iya sake fita ba sakamakon yadda bai iya fita daga nan.
Ya bambanta da rawar raƙuma a cikin watsa MERS-CoV, rawar pangolins, idan akwai wani, a cikin watsawar SARS-CoV-2 ya bambanta.
Musamman ma kwayoyin cutar jemagen pangolin beta-CoVs wanda sun fi rayuwa a jikin jemagun pangolins.
Zasu iya zama mafakar karshe ga SARS-CoV-2-beta-CoVs masu dangantaka, da kama da dabbobin civets a yanayin SARS-CoV.
Yawancin yuwuwar watsuwa tsakanin jinsuna na SARS-CoV-2 daga dabbobi zuwa mutane dole ne a yi watsi da su ko a amince da su a nazari gaba.
Na farko, jemagu za su iya zama babban reshin raunin da ke da alaƙa da ƙwayar SARS-CoV-2 kusan iri ɗaya ce ga SARS-CoV-2.
Yan-Adam na iya hadakar muhalli tare da jemagu ta hanyar yankan nama ko kuma hakar kwal.
Na biyu, pangolins na iya zama ɗayan tsaka-tsakin fadadawa wanda aka gabatar da sabon ƙwayar cuta ta SARS-CoV-2.
Yan-Adam suna kamuwa da kwayar cutar ta fannin yanka da cin naman dabba.
Yana yiwuwa yawancin dabbobi masu shayarwa ciki har da dabbobin gida suna da saukin kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2.
Lallai ne akwai bukatar gudanar da wani bincike kan dabbobin cikin gida da kuma na dawa/daji domin kariya ga jiki.
Na uku, kamar yadda aka ambata a sama, sake sakewa da daidaitawa da SARS-CoV-2 na iya faruwa a cikin jinsin na uku wanda ke da alaƙa tare da jemage da kuma pangolins.
Binciken asalin SARS-CoV-2 daga dabba har yanzu ana kan yi.
Baya ga mabanbanta dabbobin da ke daukar cutar, akwai wasu ababuwa uku muhimmai game da cutar wajen tsallakawa da halittun CoVs daga masu hana su fita.
Da farko dai, yawan adadin su na maye gurbi a cikin rabawar RNA.
Idan aka kwatanta da sauran ƙwayoyin RNA guda ɗaya, masu ƙididdigar adadin maye gurbi na CoVs za'a iya ɗauka su azaman “Matsakaici” zuwa “babba” tare da matsakaicin sauyawa mai aiki wanda ya zama ~ 10-4 sauyawa a kowace shekara ta rukunin yanar gizon 2, gwargwadon tsarin karbuwa na CoV zuwa runduna mai labari.
CoVs suna da hujjar sake-karantar exoribonuclease, sharewa wanda yake haifar da babban rikitarwa sosai da rashiwa ko mara dorewa.
Sai dai abin sha’awa a nan, asalin halittar cutar wanda galibi yake takura kwayar CoV ta hanyar haduwa da miyau ta sinadaran RNA.
Remdesivir yana daya daga cikin masu ba da rigakafin maganin SARS-CoV-2 da za a gwada su a gwajin asibiti.
Ko yaya dai, yawan maye gurbi na CoVs ya ninka sau miliyan sama da na ƙungiyar sojojinsu.
Bugu da kari, yawan maye gurbi yakan zama mafi girma yayin da CoVs ba su dace da mai zama da su ba.
Idan aka kwatanta da SARS-CoV da babban maye gurbi, adadin maye gurbi na SARS-CoV-2 na kasa sosai, bayar da shawarar mafi girman matakin karbuwa ga mutane.
Wataƙila, an riga an saba da shi ga wata mai zama da cutar da ke kusa da mutane.
Baya ga SARS-CoV-2, wannan kuma ya shafi MERS-CoV, wanda ya dace da raƙuma masu tozo guda.
A ka’idodi, ba lallai bane cewa tsaran kwayoyin halitta zai iya samar da alluran rigakafi da rigakafi akan SARS-CoV-2 marasa tasiri da sauri.
Na biyu kuma, babbar kwayar halittar RNA a jikin cutar CoVs ya nuna asalin sauyawa da rikida da tushen kwayoyin halitta suke yi, wanda hakan ke kara haifar da bazuwarsu tsakanin halittu wanda ya taimaka wajen bullar cututtukan CoVs masu shuhura a lokacin da suka samu dacewar yanayin da suke so.
Wannan yana da goyan bayan yalwar budaddun faifan karatu na musamman da amfanin furotin mai lamba ta wurin ƙarshen 3′ na genome.
Na uku, Covs na iya canza jiki barkatai da akai-akai lokacin rabuwar RNA ta hanyar “kwafin-zabi” na musamman.
A cikin mafakar da take zama wurin gaurayuwa, canzawar sassa yana faruwa akai-akai a lokacin kwafar CoV RNA.
Cigaba da cikakken-tsawon da bangarn genomic na RNAs mai sake haduwa don samar da sabbin abubuwan CoV.
An samu shaidar asalin halitta daga yadda aka halicce take a jikin duka HCoV-HKU1 da kuma HCoV-OC43, har ma da jikin dabbobi CoVs kamar su jemagu SL-CoV da batCoV-HKU9.
Mu’amalar kwayar cuta daga inda take zama da kuma na yadda take bazuwa.
Baya ga abubuwa guda uku da aka ambata a sama game da kwayar cutar, hulɗar kwayar cuta tare da mafaka mai karba wani abu ne dake tasiri akan watsuwa tsakanin jinsunar kwayar halittar.
Anan, an sake haɗawa da SARS-CoV a zaman misali na yau da kullum, wanda kuma ya nuna tabbataccen zaɓi na ɗabi'a yayin watsuwa tsakanin jinsuna.
Ta la'akari da gwajin kwatanci tsakanin keɓaɓɓun abu na SARS-CoVs din ɗan-adam da civet, Ana tunanin SARS-CoV zai iya yin saurin daidaituwa cikin mafaka daban-daban, musamman tare da maye gurbi a cikin furotin RBD na S.
Gabaɗaya, RBD a cikin furotin na S na CoV yana hulɗa tare da tantanin halita mai karban sako da mai martini abin kare jiki.
A cikin SARS-CoV, RBD yana cikin 318th zuwa 510 na amino acid din akan gungun S1, wanda ya daure wa dan Adam ACE2 kazalika hade da mai karban don shigar kwayar cuta.
RBD na SARS-CoV yana da ikon sanin masu karɓar ACE2 na dabbobi daban-daban, gami da jemage, civet, bera da karen raccoon, wadda ke ba da izinin watsuwa tsakanin jinsuna kwayar cutar.
A zahiri, amino acid guda 6 ne kawai da aka lura ya bambanta da na mutum kuma ƙwayar civet viral ta ware a cikin RBD kuma 4 daga cikinsu suna cikin motsi mai ɗaukar abubuwa don hulɗa da mai karɓar ACE2.
SARS-CoV na dabba Sivet yana da rikice-rikicen K479N da S487T a cikin RBD, wanda zai iya ƙara kusancin hulɗa da ma'adinin furotin tare da mai karɓar ACE2 na mutum.
A takaice dai, wadannan maye gurbi na amino acid na iya zama mai matukar mahimmanci ga karbar kwayar cuta a jikin mutum.
Abin lura ne cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana raba tantanin halita mai karban sako (cellular receptor) iri daya da SARS-CoV.
Bambanci kashi 30% tsakanin SARS-CoV-2 da SARS-CoV a cikin sashin S1 na furotin S yana nuna cewa ƙarshen dangantakar S furotin da dan adam ACE2 zai iya canzawa.
Tabbas, binciken cryo-EM yana nuna dangantakar mafi girma ta 10 zuwa 20 daga wannan abin da aka ɗauka sama da wanda ke tsakanin ɗan adam na ACE2 da furotin na SARS-CoV S.
Hakanan zai kasance mai ban sha'awa don sanin ko za a buƙaci kowane sauran abokin karba don watsuwar SARS-CoV-2.
Mai ban sha'awa, HCoV-NL63 kuma yana ɗaure wa ACE2 amma tare da wani sashi na S.
Akwai sauran masu karɓar HCoV, kamar aminopeptidase N don HCoV-229E, da acid 9-O-acetylated sialic acid don HCoV-OC43.
Zasu iya dauka nauyin samun nasarar daidaita wadatar waɗannan CoVs a cikin mutane bayan watsa nau'in halittu daga wurin dakaru dabbobin su.
Baya ga tantanin halita mai karban sako, sakamakon watsuwar HCoVs ta tsakanin jinsuna shi ma ana sarrafa shi ta hanyar sauran abubuwan dogaro na mafaka da abubuwan ƙuntatawa.
Rarraba waɗannan sunadaran masu kariya tsakanin ɗan adam da rarar halitta na rukunin HCoVs kamar jemagu, raƙumi da bera na iya zama cikas ga watsawar ma'amala.
HCoVs dole su rinjayi dogaro kan mafaka sannan su fi karfin ƙuntatawar mafakarsu don nasarar watsuwa tsakanin jinsina daban-daban.
Dangane da wannan, masu fayyace kwayoyin halitta a wannan muhimmin fannin na hulɗar kwayar cuta da mafakarta sun kasance har yanzu ana gano su kuma za a iya sanin su.
Binciken yanayin rashin daidaituwa game da dogaro na mafaka da abubuwan ƙuntatawa don SARS-CoV-2 ta amfani da fasahar zamani ta CRISPR na iya zama mai amfani.
Fitowar HCoVs: Koma baya ga sifili
Bambancin CoVs na jemage yana bayar da isasshe dama ga fitowar sabon HCoVs da ke daban.
Bisa wannan hujjar, cututtukan jemage na CoVs sune tushen cututtukan HCoVs.
Bugu da kari, saurin maye gurbi da sake halittar gado shima yana fitar da cigaban HCoV kuma yana zama matakai biyu masu mahimmanci a wannan aikin.
Alal misali, siyarwa ko asarar kwayoyin halittar furotin dana duniya suna da damar canza kwayar cutar kwayar halitta ta wata hanya.
Daga cikin furotin na kariya na SARS-CoV, ORF8 ana tsammanin yana da mahimmanci a cikin dacewa da mutane, kamar yadda SARS-CoV masu hade da ƙwayoyin cuta jemage wanda aka keɓancewa amma an sami sinadarai masu bambam da furotin na ORF8.
An gano rugujewar kwayar halittar 29 daga yanayin SARS-CoVs a jini a farkon lokacin da aka fara gano annobar a jikin dan adam.
Wannan sharewa ta shiga ORF8 zuwa ORF8a da ORF8b kuma ana zaton shine maye gurbi wanda yake inganta canjin mafaka.
Bayan haka, SARS-CoV yana da yiwuwar sake duba tarihin tare da layin alpha- da gamma-CoVs, inda aka gano yawancin adadin yankuna masu rarrafe a cikin polymrase ɗin RNA da suke dogara da RNA.
An kuma gano wuraren sake canzawa a cikin nsp9, mafi yawan nsp10, da kuma sassan nsp14.
