Kayayyakin kariya wato Personal Protective Equipent (PPE) ana ganin kamar baida karfin kariya amma zai taimaka wajen rage wata cutar, amma zai iya rage kamuwa da cutan.
Duk na’uin PPE dole a zabe su kafin hadarin ya afku ga ma’aikaci, asa shi yadda ya kamata (Ms. abin numfashi), asahi akoda yaushe kuma da kyau, kuma a rika duba shi akai-akai, a kuma canja idan ya kama kuma a cire, a wanke, a addana shi da kyau don gudun shina ya jirkita.
