Wanda hadarin yafi akansu sune aikin gidan ajiye gawa sun hada da ma’aikaci wadanda ke gyara gawakin mutanen da aka san su ko ana ganin kamar suna dauke da COVID-19 a lokacin mutuwar su; wadanan suna da hadari sosai idan sun gwada gawan. Karin sarrafawar injiniya a wadannan rukuni masun hadarin cutar ya hada da dakunan kebe wadanda suka kamu da cutar ko wadanda ake zato suna da COVID-19 duk lokacin ka’idar fesawar aerosl wato aerosol-generating procedures.
Na’urar bada iska na musamman ya kan iya zaman daidai a wasu wuraren kiwo lafiya wuraren dakunan ajiye gawaki.
Ya kamata a rike dukan samfura da matakan kariya uku na lafiyar halita wato Biosafety Level 3 prcaution.
Hukumar lafiya ta duniya (WHO) sun bada shawarar cewa a kebe sabbin marasa lafiya a wasu wurare daban zai dangata ko wani ne wanda ya kamu da cutar COVID-19.. Bugu da kari zuwa wasu PPE, OSHA an shawarta yin amfani da na’urar bada iska ga wadanda suke aiki tsakanin kafa 6 ga marasa lafiyan da aka sani ko wanda ake gani na da cutar, SARS-COV-2, da wadanda ke yin ka’idar fesawar aerosl wato aerosol-generating procedures.
A kasar Amurka, NIOSH ta amince da N95 don tace abin numfashi ko ma yin amfani dasu da kyau, an samu kariya wanda ya hada da gwaji mai kyau, karantarwa da kuma gwajin asibiti.
Wasu na’uran iska suna iya karewa mai kyau tare da inganta jin dadin ma’aikata. WHO ba ta amince yin amfani da kabido ba, don COVID-19 ciwon ne na hanyar numfashi wanda ke yaduwa ta hanyar ruwan jiki.
WHO ta shawarta cewa abun rufe fuska na asibiti ya dace ga ma’aikan dubawa don point-of-entry.
Ga wadanda ke karban samfuring gwajin hanyar numfashi daga, lura wa, ko tafiyar da wanda ya kamu da COVID-19 ba tare da ka’idar fesawar aerosl ba wato aerosol-generating procedure, WHO ta shawarta cewa, abin rufe fuskar tiyata, tabarau, ko garkuwar fuska, babban riga, da safar hannu.
Idan an bi ka’idar fesawar aerosl wato aerosol-generating akayi, zai mayar da gurbin amfani da abin rufe fuskar asibiti wato N95 ko abin numfashi FFP2.
Ganin cewa wadatarwar PPE a duniya bai isa ba, WHO ta ba da shawarar rage buƙatar PPE ta hanyar ba da magunguna ta hanyar sadarwa, shinge na jiki kamar wani budadeyar abun rufe fuska, barin waɗanda ke da hannu cikin kulawa kai tsaye su shiga daki da mai kamu da cutar COVID-19 yake, yin amfani da PPE kawai don takamaiman aikin, ci gaba da amfani da na’urar bada iska wanda aka saba ba tare da cire shi ba yayin da kulawa da marasa lafiya da yawa da cuta iri daya, lura da daidaita wadatarwar yawan PPE, da kuma hana amfani da abin rufe fuska ga mutane da suke da alamar cutar.
