Juyawar b’Angiotensin enzyme na 2 (ACE2) wani enzyme ne wanda aka haɗe zuwa saman farfajiya (membranes cell) na sel a cikin huhu, arteries, zuciya, koda, da hanji.
ACE2 yana ƙididdige ayyukan aikin enzyme mai alaƙa da haɗin gwiwa (ACE) ta hanyar rage yawan ƙwayar angiotensin-II da haɓaka Ang (1-7) yana sanya shi manufa mai mahimmanci don magance cututtukan zuciya. ACE2 kuma yana aiki azaman hanyar shiga cikin sel don wasu coronaviruses.
Irin ra’ayi enzyme na dan Adam ana kiransa hACE2.
Ingantaccen enzyme na Angiotensin 2 shine zinc wanda ke dauke da ironloenzyme wanda yake a saman endothelial da sauran sel.
Abubuwan gina jiki na ACE2 ya ƙunshi yanki na N-terminal peptidase M2 da yankin C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transportar domain.
ACE2 nau'ikan furotin membrane ne mai wucewa, tare da yanki mai aiki na enzymatically wanda yake fallasa saman sel a cikin huhu da sauran kyallen jiki.
Yankin extracellular na ACE2 an barke shi daga yanki mai ƙwayar cuta ta wani enzyme da aka sani da zubar da jini, kuma sakamakon furotin mai narkewa ana fitar dashi cikin magudanar jini kuma a ƙarshe ya kasance cikin fitsari.
ACE2 yana nan cikin yawancin gabobin: ACE2 na haɗu da fatar mafi yawa nau’in huhu II na tantanin halitar alveolar, enterocytes na ƙananan hanji, jijiya da ƙwayoyin jijiyoyin tantanin halita na zuciya da kuma ƙwayoyin tsoka mai laushi a cikin yawancin gabobin.
ACE2 MRNA bayanana ana iya samun su a cerebral cortex, straitum hypotamalamus da briainstem.
Aikin farko na ACE2 shine tsaya a matsayin daidaita ma'auni ga ACE.
ACE ta kuntatawa angiotensin I hormone cikin vasoconstricting angiotensin II.
ACE2 bi da bi ya kuntatawa da carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) da hydrolyses shi cikin vasodilator angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg -Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 na iya share wasu peptides da suka hada da [des-Arg9] -bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, da ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma yana daidaita fataucin membrane na tsaka mai ɗaukar amino acid SLC6A19 kuma yana da nasaba da cutar ta Hartnup.
A matsayin transmembrane furotin, ACE2 na aiki a matsayin babban hanyar shiga cikin tantanin halita (Cell) ga wasu coronavirus, hade da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (kwayar cuta da ke haifar da SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (kwayar cuta da ke haifar da COVID-19).
